# Bob Sessions

This folder stores AI assistant session history and conversation logs.

## Purpose
Keep track of your interactions with Bob (the AI assistant) for:
- Session continuity
- Historical reference
- Workflow improvements
- Learning from past conversations

## Usage
Session files will be automatically created here when using Bob to process your work notes.

## File Naming Convention
- `session_YYYY-MM-DD_HHMM.json` - JSON format session logs
- `conversation_YYYY-MM-DD.md` - Markdown format conversation history

## Privacy Note
These files are for your personal use. Add them to .gitignore if you don't want to share session history publicly.